title: DDFP 269: World Cup talk with Broncos Julius Thomas
itunes:title: DDFP 269: World Cup talk with Broncos Julius Thomas
description:
Shek, soccer enthusiast The Gold Standard and Producer Black Tie break down the latest action from World Cup including Team USA vs. Portugal, Messi vs. Cristiano Ronaldo and the tournament's best goals so far. The guys also chat with Denver Broncos tight end and avid World Cup viewer Julius Thomas about his best players and moments from the group stage and which NFL players could play soccer. It's a top-corner episode, take a listen won't you?
